data.description: Welcome to 112 Waverly Way, this home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms with a loft, perfect for a comfortable and modern living space. With the open concept design makes this home great for entertaining. The large kitchen has ample storage, granite countertops, large island with breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs is where you will find all of the bedrooms. The owner's suite has a private bath with double vanities, separate garden tub, tile shower and walk in closet. The laundry upstairs adds convenience to your daily routine. The home also features a fenced, private backyard, making it ideal for summer cookouts or just hanging out with family and friends. The home is perfectly situated near the neighborhood amenities. not to mention a short drive to Tanger mall, restaurants and other entertainment options. You are also close to downtown Savannah where you can stroll through the historic district, take a walk on River street or just hang out at Forsyth Park.
